data.description: Beautifully private 3/2 home ideal for families seeking privacy. This charming residence boasts two spacious decks, a small yet exceptional community, and sits on 1.4 acres of perfectly level land. The fireplace is in pristine condition, creating a cozy atmosphere. Additionally, the property is equipped with strong and reliable underground fiber optic cable. To further streamline the closing process, The owner is offering financing. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity for a tranquil and seamless home purchase.Why This Home is Perfect for You:Experience the charm of a peaceful and secure community, tucked away from the hustle and bustle of the main road. Enjoy the utmost privacy and safety, ideal for families. Additionally, we offer owner financing, allowing you to skip the lengthy and stressful process of dealing with banks. Make your move quick and hassle-free.
